state = data.frame(state.x77,region = state.region)
x = xyplot(Population ~ region | Life.Exp , data = state,
       type = c("p", "r"),groups = Life.Exp
       ,main = "Relation between Population and region over Life.Exp"
       ,layout = c(2,1))
x

pdf("x.pdf")
